g_odvw_0::intro_card_0::headline: Maal barachuuf abdii qabda?
g_odvw_0::clip_card_0::goals[0]: Gaafadhu: Waa'ee suur-sagalee qopheessuurraatti maal barachuuf abdatta?
g_odvw_0::text_card_1::text: "Waa'ee suur-sagalee qopheessuurraatti maal barachuuf abdatta?" jedhii hiriyaakee gaafadhu.
g_odvw_0::text_card_6::text: Hin yaadda'in, muraan hundi kuusaa faayaa keessa taa'a.
g_odvw_0::text_card_3::text: Sagaleen dudduubaa jeequ baayyeen yoo jiraate, bakka haaraa barbaadi.
g_odvw_0::text_card_5::text: Yoo muraalee baayyee waraabde, maxxansuu keen dura muraa filatte qofa hambisuudhaan kan hafan haqi.
g_odvw_0::title: Maal barachuuf abdii qabda?
g_odvw_0::text_card_0::text: Tokkoon tokkoon keessan bilbila keessaniin, gaaffiif deebii hiriyaa keessanii wajjin geggeessaa, isa booda gaaffiif deebii innimmoo sii wajjin geggeessa.
g_odvw_0::text_card_2::text: Akka hiriyaakee dhageessutti itti dhiyaachuukee mirkaneeffadhu.
